y didn't lose consciousness during this episode, but it lasted about 20 minutes before they came to the casualty department.","dimension":9,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.103,0.16772,0.1422,0.1145,0.088145,0.076028,0.069639,0.05978,0.052697,0.047339,0.043058,0.035892],"unified_progress":[0.10571,0.13466,0.10917,0.1039,0.087867,0.087074,0.075484,0.079297,0.067271,0.05931,0.050435,0.039813]},{"section":6,"text":"After getting diphenhydramine HCI, they improved quickly.","dimension":0,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.061865,0.12032,0.12593,0.11317,0.10242,0.092983,0.086702,0.076839,0.067876,0.061045,0.051069,0.039788],"unified_progress":[0.094634,0.12931,0.10986,0.106,0.091716,0.091273,0.078128,0.080751,0.07052,0.058648,0.049543,0.039611]},{"section":7,"text":"First, I know that haloperidol is a typical antipsychotic, often used for schizophrenia or other psychotic disorders.","dimension":11,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.055722,0.095457,0.10116,0.1006,0.09746,0.093241,0.092656,0.085319,0.080042,0.077645,0.065768,0.054934],"unified_progress":[0.061138,0.092765,0.10076,0.10474,0.098036,0.098896,0.091643,0.086759,0.077876,0.076364,0.061359,0.049664]},{"section":8,"text":"It's an antipsychotic that's also used for its potential to cause extrapyramidal symptoms, which include things like tardive dyskinesia, a movement disorder.","dimension":2,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.034187,0.057502,0.075947,0.08583,0.10178,0.10763,0.10872,0.10934,0.10342,0.087829,0.069643,0.058173],"unified_progress":[0.038426,0.065733,0.092575,0.098159,0.10338,0.11391,0.10447,0.09884,0.090482,0.082441,0.06385,0.047735]},{"section":9,"text":"But in this case, the symptoms are acute and seem to occur within a short timeframe after starting the medication.","dimension":9,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.067924,0.084289,0.084705,0.086591,0.083829,0.084927,0.088621,0.086757,0.086291,0.087228,0.082261,0.0